Property Details

The “config-interval” property

  “config-interval”          guint

Send Config Insertion Interval in seconds (configuration headers will be multiplexed in the data stream when detected.) (0 = disabled).

Flags: Read / Write

Allowed values: <= 3600

Default value: 0
